<p><a href="http://blitzgames.com" target="_blank">Blitz Games</a> have developed a Shrek Alarm Clock in conjunction with <a href="http://dreamworksanimation.com" target="_blank">DreamWorks</a>. It's the first of its kind which allows anyone to be woken up and interact with everyone's favourite ogre! For the application to be shown to the world, the team at <a href="http://blitzgamesstudios.com" target="_blank">Blitz Games Studios</a> required a website where they're able to explain the app and provide links to the relevant download stores.</p>
